# Plugin packaging exclusions (Phase 9 INST-03)
# These files are tracked in git but excluded from marketplace plugin install
# since Claude Code plugin install clones via git respecting .gitignore
# NOTE: Per research, .gitignore excludes from `git clone` used by marketplace.
# However, these are tracked files. Research open question 3 concluded:
# "Do NOT gitignore tracked directories... accept that plugin cache includes
# these files (they're small text files, not a size concern)."
# The important exclusions (.venv, __pycache__, output, lib) are already above.
node_modules/
